data.description: Charming ranch in the village limits. Close to town and all the amenities.  Three bedrooms and 1-1/2 bath in this nice area near Palmer Lake.  These two lots offers a lot of space for you to have fun and a  full basement waiting tor you to finish.  Two fireplaces for your cooler evenings.  Outside fire pit allows for wonderful evenings outside.  Take a look and see for yourself.  Square footage, taxes and measurements are all estimate. Please verify.  Taxes will change upon a sale. Seller is motivated and will look at all offers.  Seller might consider a carpet allowance.
